### AgentRegistryApi HTTP Test Cases
### Base URL: http://localhost:8080
### All endpoints accept JSON and return JSON responses

### ============================================================
### 1. Agent Registration Endpoint
### POST /api/v1/scheduler/register
### ============================================================

### Test Case 1.1: Successful Agent Registration
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/scheduler/register
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Basic {{username}} {{password}}

{
  "agentId": "agent-001",
  "name": "Test Agent 001",
  "agentUrl": "http://localhost:9091",
  "maxConcurrentTasks": 5,
  "maxPendingTasks": 10,
  "supportedExecutionKeys": ["shell", "python", "java"]
}

### Test Case 1.2: Registration with Minimal Required Fields
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/scheduler/register
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Basic {{username}} {{password}}

{
    "agentId": "agent-002",
    "name": "Test Agent 002",
    "agentUrl": "http://localhost:9092",
    "maxConcurrentTasks": 3,
    "supportedExecutionKeys": ["java", "shell"]
}

### Test Case 1.3: Duplicate Registration (Should Reactivate Existing)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/scheduler/register
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Basic {{username}} {{password}}

{
  "agentId": "agent-001",
  "name": "Test Agent 001 - Updated",
  "agentUrl": "http://localhost:9091",
  "maxConcurrentTasks": 8,
  "maxPendingTasks": 20,
  "supportedExecutionKeys": ["shell", "python", "java", "go"]
}

### Test Case 1.4: Invalid Registration - Missing agentId
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/scheduler/register
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Basic {{username}} {{password}}

{
  "name": "Invalid Agent",
  "agentUrl": "http://localhost:9093",
  "maxConcurrentTasks": 5
}

### Test Case 1.5: Invalid Registration - Empty agentId
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/scheduler/register
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Basic {{username}} {{password}}

{
  "agentId": "",
  "name": "Invalid Agent",
  "agentUrl": "http://localhost:9093",
  "maxConcurrentTasks": 5
}

