### ============================================================
### Performance and Load Testing Scenarios
### ============================================================

### Note: These tests are designed for load testing tools like k6 or JMeter
### Below are example requests that can be used as templates

### Rapid Status Updates (Simulate High Frequency Heartbeats)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/scheduler/report_status
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "agentId": "load-test-agent",
  "running": true,
  "pendingTasks": 0,
  "runningTasks": 0,
  "finishedTasks": 1000,
  "maxConcurrentTasks": 10,
  "maxPendingTasks": 20
}

###

### Bulk Task Results Report
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/scheduler/report_result
Content-Type: application/json

[
  {
    "agentId": "load-test-agent",
    "taskId": 10001,
    "success": true,
    "output": "{\"batch\": 1, \"item\": 1}",
    "endTime": "2025-04-27T13:00:00Z"
  },
  {
    "agentId": "load-test-agent",
    "taskId": 10002,
    "success": true,
    "output": "{\"batch\": 1, \"item\": 2}",
    "endTime": "2025-04-27T13:00:01Z"
  },
  {
    "agentId": "load-test-agent",
    "taskId": 10003,
    "success": true,
    "output": "{\"batch\": 1, \"item\": 3}",
    "endTime": "2025-04-27T13:00:02Z"
  }
]

###

### ============================================================
### Response Format Reference
### ============================================================

### Success Response (HTTP 200 OK):
### {
###   "code": 200,
###   "message": "Operation successful message",
###   "timestamp": 1714215600000,
###   "data": null
### }

### Error Response (HTTP 400 Bad Request):
### {
###   "code": 400,
###   "message": "Error description",
###   "timestamp": 1714215600000,
###   "data": null
### }

### ============================================================
### End of Test Cases
### ============================================================
